Description_lang: Chains two enemy targets together. While the targets are over ${$m1/$m3} yds apart the chains inflict $M3 Fire damage every $t1 sec. This damage increases by $s2% each second they remain apart. The chains will break if the targets remain apart for $u total seconds.
AuraDescription_lang: ${(($m2/100)*($M3/$m3))+($M3/$m3)} Fire damage inflicted if over ${$m1/$m3} yds from linked player.Damage increases ${$m2/$m3}% per stack.Breaks at $u stacks.
